tip.text: The miso Kurobuta and the scallops in Japanese butter are winners. Try the tres leches for excellent dessert.
The space is fantastic - inviting, cozy and tasteful. Have the Black Onyx, via Chemex. It'sstrong and delicious, with interesting notes of cocoa and butter.
If you're going to eat only one thing here, choose the lamb duet salad: Field greens, roast lamb strips, lamb fat crisps, dried apricot, mint vinaigrette. Just exquisite.
The pork tacos and shrimp tacos are standouts. They're still in soft opening mode so the service can be generously described as "in beta"
Easy to understand why this is Asia's #1 ranked restaurant. Standouts include the swimmer crab curry, the steamed coral trout and the stir fried pak warn with chili.
